Enhancement: Adjust share management to properly work with spaces

This includes the following changes:

* Added a new method `shareSpaceWithUser`
* Added the possibility to pass URL params to the `deleteShare` method
* Added a new `space_ref` param when fetching or adding new shares

https://github.com/owncloud/owncloud-sdk/pull/1013
https://github.com/owncloud/owncloud-sdk/pull/1025
https://github.com/owncloud/owncloud-sdk/pull/1027
